ActPhysical Activity and Sport Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Canadian Heritage as the Minister for the Purposes of the Physical Activity and Sport Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-782 of July 26, 2023; and (2) designating the Minister of CANADIAN HERITAGE, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the PHYSICAL ACTIVITY AND SPORT ACT.
